# EU_02 Custom Service Definition: Add.srv
# Location: my_cliserv_package_interfaces/srv/Add.srv
#
# Theory:
#   ROS2 service interfaces are defined in .srv files separated by ---:
#     Lines BEFORE --- define the REQUEST fields
#     Lines AFTER  --- define the RESPONSE fields
#
#   After building, the service is accessible in C++ as:
#     #include "my_cliserv_package_interfaces/srv/add.hpp"
#   The request and response are accessed via:
#     SrvType::Request   and   SrvType::Response

# ── Request ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
int64 a
int64 b
---
# ── Response ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
int64 sum
